item.title: Experiment
item.description: Pipeline of the experiment: How to run the experiment: Get the code Setup: Install Java 8 Install Octave 4.x Install Anaconda for Python 3.6 Install python packages: pip install umap-learn wget keras numpy pandas scikit-learn conda install -c conda-forge shogun git clone https://github.com/DmitryUlyanov/Multicore-TSNE.git cd Multicore-TSNE/ pip install . Sanity check: python test_wrappers.py python test_projections.py Getting the datasets (it will take some time.
